        <item>
        <title>使用了两年的SSD</title>
        <link>https://umi.im/2-year-ssd/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 30 Jan 2015 00:14:41 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://umi.im/2-year-ssd/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;两年前的时候花了310在淘宝购入的蓝科 X2 64GB固态硬盘，刷了金士顿SV200鸡血固件，在SATA 2下速度还可以，当时最火的镁光M4-64GB好像是500多分。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-3482&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1.png&#34; alt=&#34;2-year-ssd-1&#34; width=&#34;503&#34; height=&#34;502&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1.png 503w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1-150x150.png 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1-300x300.png 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd-1-80x80.png 80w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;中等强度使用两年后，写入只有可能的4MB/s…C4的TF卡的速度…竟然还没挂…不可思议…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2-year-ssd.png&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
